{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"To increase the chance of placing high-priority labels on the map, you can"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provide an array of "},{"code":"textAnchor","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" locations, each paired with an offset value."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The renderer will attempt to place the label at each location, in order, before"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"moving on to the next location+offset. Use "},{"code":"textJustify: auto","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" to choose"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"justification based on anchor position."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSExpression","text":"NSExpression","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" * ","kind":"text"},{"text":"textVariableAnchorOffset","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The length of the array must be even, and must alternate between enum and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"point entries. i.e., each anchor location must be accompanied by a point, and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"that point defines the offset when the corresponding anchor location is used."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Positive offset values indicate right and down, while negative values indicate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"left and up. Anchor locations may repeat, allowing the renderer to try multiple"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"offsets to try and place a label using the same anchor."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When present, this property takes precedence over "},{"code":"textAnchor","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"textVariableAnchor","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"code":"textOffset","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", and "},{"code":"textRadialOffset","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["{ \"text-variable-anchor-offset\": [\"top\", [0, 4], \"left\", [3,0], \"bottom\", [1,","1]] } "],"syntax":"json","type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When the renderer chooses the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"top"},{"type":"text","text":" anchor, "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"[0, 4]"},{"type":"text","text":" will be used for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textOffset"},{"type":"text","text":"; the text will be shifted down by 4 ems."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When the renderer chooses the "},{"code":"left","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" anchor, "},{"code":"[3, 0]","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" will be used for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"textOffset","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"; the text will be shifted right by 3 ems."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"This property is only applied to the style if ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"text"},{"text":" is non-","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"text":", and","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"symbolPlacement"},{"text":" is set to an expression that evaluates to or","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"MLNSymbolPlacementPoint"},{"text":". Otherwise, it is ignored.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"You can set this property to an expression containing any of the following:","type":"text"}],"type"